SET NOCOUNT ON;
MERGE [ElementType] USING (
VALUES (@p0, 0),
(@p1, 1),
(@p2, 2)) AS i ([Name], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Name])
VALUES (i.[Name])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position;
MERGE [Generation] USING (
VALUES (@p3, @p4, 0),
(@p5, @p6, 1)) AS i ([Name], [Number], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Name], [Number])
VALUES (i.[Name], i.[Number])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position;

CREATE TABLE [IdempotencyKey] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [ExternalKey] nvarchar(128) NOT NULL,
    [PayloadHash] nvarchar(64) NOT NULL,
    [CreatedUtc] datetime2 NOT NULL,
    [ResponseBody] nvarchar(max) NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_IdempotencyKey] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [SystemConfig] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [State] nvarchar(16) NOT NULL,
    [SyncInProgress] bit NOT NULL,
    [BootstrapInProgress] bit NOT NULL,
    [LastSyncUtc] datetimeoffset NULL,
    [LastSyncError] nvarchar(2000) NULL,
    [UpdatedAtUtc] datetimeoffset NOT NULL DEFAULT (SYSUTCDATETIME()),
    [RowVersion] rowversion NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_SystemConfig] PRIMARY KEY ([Id])
);

CREATE TABLE [Pokemon] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [Name] nvarchar(100) NOT NULL,
    [ExternalId] nvarchar(32) NOT NULL,
    [Number] int NOT NULL,
    [GenerationId] int NOT NULL,
    [SpriteUrl] nvarchar(512) NOT NULL,
    [Height] decimal(6,2) NOT NULL,
    [Weight] decimal(7,2) NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_Pokemon] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_Pokemon_Generation_GenerationId] FOREIGN KEY ([GenerationId]) REFERENCES [Generation] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION
);

CREATE TABLE [PokemonFlavor] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [PokemonId] int NOT NULL,
    [Language] nvarchar(8) NOT NULL,
    [Text] nvarchar(4000) NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_PokemonFlavor] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_PokemonFlavor_Pokemon_PokemonId] FOREIGN KEY ([PokemonId]) REFERENCES [Pokemon] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [PokemonStat] (
    [Id] int NOT NULL IDENTITY,
    [PokemonId] int NOT NULL,
    [StatName] nvarchar(32) NOT NULL,
    [BaseValue] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_PokemonStat] PRIMARY KEY ([Id]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_PokemonStat_Pokemon_PokemonId] FOREIGN KEY ([PokemonId]) REFERENCES [Pokemon] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);

CREATE TABLE [PokemonType] (
    [PokemonId] int NOT NULL,
    [TypeId] int NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT [PK_PokemonType] PRIMARY KEY ([PokemonId], [TypeId]),
    CONSTRAINT [FK_PokemonType_ElementType_TypeId] FOREIGN KEY ([TypeId]) REFERENCES [ElementType] ([Id]) ON DELETE NO ACTION,
    CONSTRAINT [FK_PokemonType_Pokemon_PokemonId] FOREIGN KEY ([PokemonId]) REFERENCES [Pokemon] ([Id]) ON DELETE CASCADE
);
